name: Julie (Supernatural: Origins)
description: Julie eventually became the best friend of Mary prior to the latter's death and was saddened when upon hearing the news that her friend had died. She was visited on Thursday, November 10, 1983 where John had his sons sleep over. That night, the two talked about what had really happened with Julie believing John's story that he saw Mary die on the ceiling was due to falling asleep watching the television.
